metadata.description:
Niels presents a review of learning rules in biological neurons and deep learning neurons with a focus on Hebbian learning, spike timing dependent plasticity (STDP) and HTM neurons.

00:00 Introduction to Learning Rules in the Brain
15:20 Hebbian Learning and Inhibition
35:22 Understanding HTM Neurons and Learning Signals
37:43 Spike Timing Dependent Plasticity (STDP) Explained
45:09 Challenges and Insights in Neural Learning
